# DataScannerViewController.ScanningUnavailable.unsupported

**Case**

The data scanner isn’t supported on this device.

## Declaration

```swift
case unsupported
```

## Discussion

The device must have the Neural Engine to perform data scanning.

## Unavailable errors

- **DataScannerViewController.ScanningUnavailable.cameraRestricted**: The data scanner isn’t available due to user restrictions on the use of the camera.
